    dc:description "Figure 16. Multivariate ratio analysis for Ooencyrtus mirus sp. nov. and O. telenomicida A scatterplot of isosize against first shape PC B shape PCA, scatterplot of first against second shape PC C PCA ratio spectrum for PC 1, bars represent 68 % confidence intervals D allometry ratio spectrum; bars represent 68 % confidence intervals." ;
